<p>中分作者页最速传说！！赶紧留个言，可惜没占到第一 期待你之后的更多作品！加油啊，黑键jpg ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedreamkiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5064505); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5064505&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="TheDreamKiller" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5064505)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedreamkiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5064505); return false;">TheDreamKiller</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>回复：</strong>你也搞快点，Dr.唐的人设我还等着看呢。</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>猛地发现星凌up了你的人事（双重含义）<span style="color: white">（此处可能道歉QwQ）</span>——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6114202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="Frozen starry sky" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6114202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;">Frozen starry sky</a></span></p>
