<p><strong>回复：</strong>这竟然是我发布的第一个没被星凌d的界面，不胜荣幸！<span style="color: white">回白字：不，其实我不介意的，觉得文档不符合标准的时候就应该d。当然如果能留下改进意见就更好啦。</span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>是怪物新人！我爱了爱了——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5526785&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="BruceWu0463" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5526785)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;">BruceWu0463</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>回复：</strong>没有没有，我写得像屎（。）前辈什么时候开个二阶段稿楼啊！</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>回复：</strong>二阶段只有半个月了还有稿楼的必要吗.jpg——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;">Kcorena</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>与之相比我就是一条真正的咸鱼。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6331978); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6331978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="carter lu" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6331978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6331978); return false;">carter lu</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>回复：</strong>前辈不要说笑了，上过精品的作者怎么能叫咸鱼（。</p>
<hr />
<p><strong>回复：</strong>你记错了吧，我没上过精品。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6331978); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6331978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="carter lu" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6331978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6331978); return false;">carter lu</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>回复：</strong>会不会以为你的李家庄上精了（——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;">Kcorena</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>回复：</strong>我记错了。太丢人了我爬！！</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>本来没想留言，但好像是第一次看到用留言板互动的形式，之前看到的都是别人单方面留言而作者什么也不说。这种互动形式真的有意思，一下子没忍住就。截至目前键斯特绝对可以说是高产高质量作者，与之相比我就是一条真正的咸鱼.jpg——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;">Kcorena</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>回复：</strong>说来好笑，其实我是因为不喜欢评论区互动刷板，但是又觉得不回复诸位不太好，所以才设了留言板（。）这么一看效果还不错，欢迎大家以后继续和我留言板互动！</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>与之相比我就是一条真正的咸鱼。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hoah2333" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4915183); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4915183&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="hoah2333" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4915183)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hoah2333" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4915183); return false;">hoah2333</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>回复：</strong>诸位前辈别硼了，人都被硼傻了，我一会就把这页归档。</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(7027379); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=7027379&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="Keyest" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=7027379)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/keyest" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(7027379); return false;">Keyest</a></span>：生存即繁衍，我即番茄汤。</p>
