<blockquote>
<p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chroiridium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6213424); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6213424&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="ChroIridium" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6213424)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chroiridium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6213424); return false;">ChroIridium</a></span>：不由感慨自己是个什么样的贵物。</p>
