</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/franz-ismal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6351354); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6351354&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610128494" alt="Franz Ismal" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6351354)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/franz-ismal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6351354); return false;">Franz Ismal</a></span>：键鱼前辈真的好厉害……发文的速度还是质量啥的咱都望尘莫及……哎呀呀，嫉妒心，旺盛起来了！</p>
